    <briefdescription>
<para>Describes a font size range for range-based text fit. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1Text" kindref="compound">Text</ref> fit selects the largest font size within the configured range that fits into the available layout space.</para>
<para><ref refid="namespaceDali_1_1Ui_1_1Text" kindref="compound">Text</ref> fit searches within the configured range using the specified font size step to find the largest fitting size.</para>
<para>The line height is not specified by this object. It follows the current text style configuration, including the configured line height mode and value.</para>
<para>This object is used to configure text fit behavior. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
